WEBVTT

00:03.141 --> 00:04.812
So what do you want to get, Susie?

00:05.413 --> 00:09.429
I want to get a couple of shirts and maybe a pair of pants as well.

00:09.698 --> 00:10.637
How about these?

00:11.052 --> 00:12.363
I think they'd look good on you.

00:12.696 --> 00:15.377
No, I don't think those are what I'm looking for.

00:15.705 --> 00:17.655
What kind of shirts are you looking for?

00:18.118 --> 00:19.937
Something that will be good for the summer.

00:20.095 --> 00:22.716
You know, shortsleeved or even sleeveless.

00:23.067 --> 00:24.715
Here, these look nice.

00:24.951 --> 00:26.928
Why don't you try on a couple of these?

00:27.241 --> 00:28.307
Which do you prefer?

00:28.651 --> 00:29.991
This shirt or that one?

00:30.403 --> 00:31.902
I think I'd choose this shirt.

